<!-- SLIDE 3: Results -->
<section class="slide" data-notes="This is what BVIF produced for Precision Furniture. The initiative started as a plain-language idea — predictive maintenance using machine learning on sensor data — and BVIF converted it into $9.36M in quantified annual business value. Breakdown: (1) Recovered production capacity — $6.46M/year from cutting unplanned downtime in half (2.8% → 1.4%), recovering 162 hours per quarter at $9,971 lost contribution margin per hour. (2) Maintenance cost reduction — $1.73M/year from a 20% reduction in maintenance cost per unit ($12.00 → $9.60) across 720,000 annual units. (3) Delivery penalty avoidance — $1.17M/year from a 5-point improvement in on-time delivery (90% → 95%), eliminating 117 late orders per quarter at $2,500 per penalty. Every figure is conservative and validated against peer case studies and industry benchmarks. Beyond the dollars, the initiative protects customer relationships, defends the mid-market position, and improves operational resilience. Emphasize: this level of rigor came from one structured workshop with the agent, grounded only in the business context the team provided.">
  <span class="eyebrow">Result · BVIF applied to Precision Furniture</span>
  <h2 class="headline">$9.36M in quantified annual business value</h2>

  <div class="row" style="flex:1; align-items:stretch;">
    <div class="col" style="flex: 1;">
      <div class="card" style="height:100%;">
        <span class="pill">Start — The idea</span>
        <div class="quote-card" style="margin-top:18px;">
          Implement a predictive maintenance system powered by machine learning that analyzes equipment sensor data from our automated lines — predicting failures before they happen and optimizing maintenance across our three facilities.
        </div>
        <ul class="bullets" style="margin-top:14px;">
          <li>Only business context — no technical detail</li>
          <li>Conservative targets, peer-validated</li>
          <li>Traceable end-to-end</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col" style="flex: 1.2;">
      <div class="card" style="height:100%; display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
        <span class="pill">End — Quantified business value</span>
        <div style="display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:16px; margin-top:14px;">
          <span class="big-value">$9.36M</span>
          <span class="muted">/year</span>
        </div>
        <div class="value-strip">
